| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7017 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8978d3f0-5655-521d-a459-33ebeb7d8cee"
